name: Misty (Pokemon)
description:
Lora model of Misty from Pokemon series, best pokegirl :) All previews done with weight 0.9 (still works fine at weight 1, but I didn't noticed -_-).

There are already some models for Misty, including this 8mb one https://civitai.com/models/8243/misty-pokemon-lora-8-mb it works very well even at that size and I made nice pictures with it :D but I also wanted to be able to do some alternative outfits so I made this model that let me do that. If you're after classic outfit, you should definitely check the 8mb one too.

List of prompts:

  • Classic outfit - misty \(pokemon\), side ponytail, suspenders, sneakers, midriff, denim shorts, yellow tank top

  • Modern outfit with white top - misty \(pokemon\), side ponytail, white tank top, midriff, denim shorts, sneakers

  • Blue swimsuit (gym leader from III gen) - misty \(pokemon\), side ponytail, blue bikini, wristband

  • Gym clothes from newer games - misty \(pokemon\), alternate hairstyle, white jacket, competition swimsuit, sandals

  • Slingshot swimsuit from manga - misty \(pokemon\), side ponytail, fingerless gloves, slingshot swimsuit, belt

  • Trouble, make it double - misty \(pokemon\), side ponytail, team rocket uniform, midriff, black thighhighs

Some other fun things you can do:

  • black hair - optionally goes together with slingshot swimsuit

  • underboob, open fly, short shorts - ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
